OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778688714
OL,3,CWhat quirky traditions will be on show
OL,4,Cfor the King's speech?
OL,6,FThe King's Speech, a key part of the
OL,7,Fstate opening of Parliament, was set
OL,8,Fto be a key element of a government
OL,9,Freset and provide a boost to Keir
OL,10,FStarmer after punishing election
OL,11,Flosses.
OL,13,FWith Starmer's premiership hanging in
OL,14,Fthe balance, the prospect of him
OL,15,Fseeing out his government's plans for
OL,16,Fnew legislation looks increasingly
OL,17,Fslim. But regardless of Starmer's
OL,18,Fposition, the business of state
OL,19,Fcontinues, and on Wednesday, the King
OL,20,Fwill unveil what the government hopes
OL,21,Fto legislate in the coming months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
