OL,3,CWhat quirky traditions will be on show
OL,4,Cfor the King's speech?
OL,6,FAlthough the full details of the
OL,7,Fpolicies in the King's speech will
OL,8,Fonly be known on the day, there is a
OL,9,Fgood idea of some of the laws the
OL,10,Fgovernment wants to pass.
OL,12,FIt is expected that a bill aimed at
OL,13,Fmeeting manifesto pledges on forcing
OL,14,Flarge firms to report ethnicity and
OL,15,Fdisability pay gaps for large
OL,16,Femployers.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
