OL,3,CWhat quirky traditions will be on show
OL,4,Cfor the King's speech?
OL,6,FAnother manifesto pledge on reforming
OL,7,Fleasehold and commonhold laws is also
OL,8,Fexpected to be in the speech.
OL,10,FTwo other high-profile reforms that
OL,11,Fmay make it into the King's speech
OL,12,Finclude the government's tightening of
OL,13,Fasylum laws and reforms to special
OL,14,Feducational needs in education.
OL,16,FThe government is also expected to
OL,17,Fintroduce its planned tightening of
OL,18,Fasylum seeker rules in the coming
OL,19,Fparliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
